{"word":"ἀλέξανδρος","slug":"ἀλέξανδρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλέξανδρος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀλέξω'><el>ἀλέξω</el></a>, <a href='S:ἀνήρ'><el>ἀνήρ</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>defending men</i>, <el>πόλεμος</el> Inscr. <a href='S:apud (quoted in)'>ap.</a> Diod.<p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>the usual name of Paris in <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b> Ag. 61, 363.<p/></div>"}]}